{"tid":556027,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藥材舖老闆娘　紅隧推車仔過海　 患認知障礙迷路　上環行到九龍","createTime":"2018-02-10T06:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T02:23:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"22f73cad3ac3a373fb6db8b0dbc8dc720af02259","tid":556027,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T06:11:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180210/20301047?_ga=2.50301350.1662121137.1517898321-581282530.1504247435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180210%2F20301047%3F_ga%3D2.50301350.1662121137.1517898321-581282530.1504247435&d=GgtnigCJUe6ZxGrt%2FZz%2Bw2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=6adb7ad6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180210%2F20301047%3F_ga%3D2.50301350.1662121137.1517898321-581282530.1504247435&h=025be922\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180210/20301047?_ga=2.50301350.1662121137.1517898321-581282530.1504247435</a><br />\n<br />\n藥材舖老闆娘　紅隧推車仔過海　<br />\n患認知障礙迷路　上環行到九龍<br />\n<br />\n6,277<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180210/large/10la8p01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180210%2Flarge%2F10la8p01.jpg&h=e8663dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 【告士打道】■婦人推着車仔由上環藥材店沿夏慤道行至告士打道，在中線旁若無人。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】上環一名62歲藥材舖女東主患有認知障礙，但為口奔馳，她仍負責送貨，昨晨用手推車送兩箱貨物往中環，途中迷失方向，沿夏慤道走入紅隧，汽車在旁邊疾馳而過，險象環生，警方聞訊在九龍出口截獲她，將她帶往警署由丈夫接走。丈夫表示打算結束藥材店全力照顧妻子。<br />\n<br />\n記者：張培生　胡恩宏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n誤闖紅隧的婦人姓陳（62歲），人稱娟姐，與姓梁丈夫在上環高陞街開樓上藥材舖，梁先生接受《蘋果》訪問時表示，與妻子結婚30多年，育有一子，3年前，見妻子記憶力嚴重衰退，求醫診斷她患有認知障礙症，原本要求她休息，但妻子熱愛工作，繼續留下幫手。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180210/large/10la8p02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180210%2Flarge%2F10la8p02.jpg&h=66e93a20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 【紅隧管道】■闖入隧道沿邊壆步行「過海」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夫：或結束間舖照顧老婆<br />\n他又說，妻子間中會送貨，為免她迷路，在身上掛有一張名牌以防萬一，列明患上甚麼病及家人聯絡電話，妻子嫌難看收於褲袋內。梁指出，今次事件反映妻子已病情不輕，由於兒子另有工作，他打算結束藥材舖生意，全力照顧妻子︰「會考慮結束間舖，日後照顧好老婆」。<br />\n昨晨10時11分，負責送貨往中環的娟姐，其間迷路失去方向，一路推着車仔沿夏慤道入紅隧，多輛汽車在旁邊駛過，極為驚險，職員發現報警。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n警員接報到場，在九龍出口截獲娟姐。由高陞街出發到現場約7公里。她的手推車上有兩箱貨物，對為何闖入紅隧管道，她一臉迷茫，警員將她送往灣仔警署調查，警員根據其身上名牌，聯絡到其丈夫，最終由丈夫接走，其夫對在場記者承認妻子患有腦退化症（認知障礙），昨早如常由店舖送貨往中環，豈料卻誤闖隧道。<br />\n<br />\n網民上載陳婦在馬路及管道情況，只見她推手推車沿灣仔告士打道中線前行，當時車輛在其旁邊駛過，陳視若無睹，及後進紅隧，沿慢線邊旁前行。有網民稱：「推手推車過紅隧收幾錢？」「真唔真吖？」根據法例，任何人未經批准擅自徒步闖入隧道區，可判罰款5,000元及監禁六個月。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180210/large/a0901a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180210%2Flarge%2Fa0901a.gif&h=8f9d98f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n健康產品騙局　2,000港人中招失4億<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n女事主或已失判斷危險能力"},{"pid":"f2faa8e51e7175e630e7b2a93e3e76795fe5bf8d","tid":556027,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T06:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457d096bfe892e334419499fefd84cc10927b8b5","tid":556027,"uid":73509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T06:18:21.000Z","msg":"原來係有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1576ce4e119c51894df889b09f0061e531282d3","tid":556027,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"457d096bfe892e334419499fefd84cc10927b8b5","tid":556027,"uid":73509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T06:18:21.000Z","msg":"原來係有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T06:23:28.000Z","msg":"咁樣推車過海...係就係一定係有病架啦不過睇下係咩病啫唔通行為藝術咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6d500d1744f4805a57bf762419964953b65a10","tid":556027,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T06:29:13.000Z","msg":"行路post巴打學野啦"},{"pid":"54bc204a068ac18d7876bf89f2c6c7e3038f70d2","tid":556027,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"佢都幾行得喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d3d244da0ad6e3fbf4f1a9bfa325104ea7c15d","tid":556027,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T06:56:34.000Z","msg":"好多隱性有錢佬會打去捐錢"},{"pid":"0c9e55968581a9ab670afb59333493c614e8e007","tid":556027,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T02:23:04.000Z","msg":"無cut 線wor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}